attributes.Long form description: The instruction is to assemble the bedside table. First, the student inspects the furniture pieces, and then he assembles the four legs to the shelf one hex socket head per leg, and then he screws the four missing hex socket heads from the legs and finishes tightening it with the allen wrench. The student flips the furniture to align the top table with the legs, and then he screws the top hex socket heads with the allen wrench, and then the student stands the furniture upright.

attributes.Transcription: We will now assemble a bedside table from IKEA. So please go ahead and assemble it.

attributes.Action sentence: The student inspects the legs of the table.
The student screws the first leg.
The student screws the second leg.
The student screws the third leg.
The student screws the fourth leg.
The student tightens the hex socket heads.
The student aligns the top table with the legs.
The student assembles the top table.
